        "title": "While-Schleifen unterbrechen",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 126872,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Bisher haben wir gelernt, wie man eine while-Schleife erstellt. Jetzt konzentrieren wir uns darauf, wie man verhindert, dass sie unendlich schleifen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Creating the variable",
            "id": 126873,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um eine Schleife zu stoppen, beginnen wir damit, eine Variable außerhalb der Schleife zu erstellen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>let</code>, gefolgt von <code>keepGoing</code> und schließlich <code>=</code>, <code>true</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variable in the condition",
            "id": 126874,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wir verwenden die Variable in der Bedingung, um zu entscheiden, ob die Schleife ihren Codeblock ausführen soll oder nicht. Zum Beispiel, <code>while keepGoing</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"36\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>keepGoing</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Updating the variable",
            "id": 126875,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Innerhalb des Codeblocks stoppen wir die Schleife, indem wir <code>keepGoing</code> auf <code>false</code> setzen, sodass die Bedingung <code>false</code> zurückgibt.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"72\" endIndex=\"77\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>false</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Stopping the loop",
            "id": 126876,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Die Schleife führt ihren gesamten Codeblock aus, weil <code>keepGoing</code> zunächst <code>true</code> ist, aber sie wird nicht erneut ausgeführt, wenn wir <code>keepGoing</code> auf <code>false</code> setzen.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: \\(keepGoing)&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: \\(keepGoing)&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"92\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"keepGoing: true\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"keepGoing: false\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Gib <code>false</code> ein.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Creating the variable",
            "id": 126877,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Woher wissen wir, dass diese Schleife läuft und nie aufhört, ihren Codeblock zu wiederholen?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Es gibt keine Variable in der Bedingung</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Diese Schleife wird nicht ausgeführt, da die Bedingung <code>false</code> ist</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Es gibt keine Variable in der Bedingung.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Variable in the condition",
            "id": 126878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Woher wissen wir, dass die <code>while</code>-Schleife ihren Codeblock überspringt?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Der Wert von <code>isLoading</code> ist <code>false</code>, aber die Bedingung überprüft, ob er <code>true</code> ist</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Der Wert von <code>isLoading</code> ist <code>false</code> und die Bedingung überprüft, ob es <code>false</code> ist</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Der Wert von <code>isLoading</code> ist <code>false</code>, aber die Bedingung überprüft, ob er <code>true</code> ist.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Updating the variable",
            "id": 126879,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Woher wissen wir, dass diese Schleife stoppt?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Just keep swimming&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Just keep swimming\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Die <code>keepGoing</code>-Variable wird innerhalb des Codeblocks auf <code>false</code> aktualisiert</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Wir wissen nicht, ob die Schleife stoppt</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Die <code>keepGoing</code>-Variable wird innerhalb des Codeblocks auf <code>false</code> aktualisiert.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Stopping the loop",
            "id": 126880,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Was zeigt dieser Code in der Konsole an?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Dolce Vita&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Dolce Vita\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>Now Playing: Dolce Vita</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Dieser Code zeigt nichts in der Konsole an</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>Now Playing: Dolce Vita</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Creating the variable",
            "id": 126881,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um die Variable in der Bedingung der while-Schleife zu verwenden, deklariere sie außerhalb des Codeblocks.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Ryan Paris&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Ryan Paris\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>var</code>, gefolgt von <code>keepPlaying</code> und schließlich <code>=</code>, <code>true</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Variable in the condition",
            "id": 126882,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Überspringe die Schleife, indem du die Variable <code>autopilotOn</code> innerhalb der Bedingung verwendest.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Autopilot on: vroom!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" autopilotOn = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"41\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>autopilotOn</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Updating the variable",
            "id": 126883,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Innerhalb des Codeblocks beende die Schleife, nachdem der Codeblock ausgeführt wurde, indem du <code>keepPlaying</code> auf <code>false</code> setzt.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Yummy&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"86\" /><option startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"92\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Yummy\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Wähle <code>keepPlaying</code>, gefolgt von <code>=</code> und schließlich <code>false</code> aus.</p></body></html>"
          },
